{"tid":1575450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"果600個醫生","createTime":"2019-09-17T01:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T14:45:07.000Z","uid":323064,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"be8515a882c5132813be1649cd14df78770bf551","tid":1575450,"uid":323064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:08:56.000Z","msg":"From HA secrets<br />\n<br />\n《600個醫生簽名支持警察》<br />\n個list 真係好好睇呀<br />\n私家醫生同老前輩佔多數<br />\n好多養X名醫<br />\n仲有一個二個中環跑馬地開店<br />\n唔知有幾多個係月入幾十萬起嘅收成期人士呢<br />\n仲有月球人，星球人有政協，建制派背景<br />\n當然仲有食女無數嘅名醫，係人都知同佢瞓一晚送一個名牌手袋，搞大同事個肚要人落仔<br />\n<br />\n再重溫下幾單經典新聞，純粹做下Medical Council嘅case studies， 如有雷同實屬巧合啦:<br />\n<br />\n私 家 西 醫 非 禮 女 病 人 罪 成(林 鴻 安 )<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/archive/fullstory.asp?andor=or&amp;year1=2000&amp;month1=6&amp;day1=1&amp;year2=2000&amp;month2=8&amp;day2=3&amp;category=a&amp;id=20000628a04&amp;keyword1=&amp;keyword2=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Farchive%2Ffullstory.asp%3Fandor%3Dor%26year1%3D2000%26month1%3D6%26day1%3D1%26year2%3D2000%26month2%3D8%26day2%3D3%26category%3Da%26id%3D20000628a04%26keyword1%3D%26keyword2%3D&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=50c69264\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Farchive%2Ffullstory.asp%3Fandor%3Dor%26year1%3D2000%26month1%3D6%26day1%3D1%26year2%3D2000%26month2%3D8%26day2%3D3%26category%3Da%26id%3D20000628a04%26keyword1%3D%26keyword2%3D&h=989f0563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/archive/fullstory.asp?andor=or&amp;year1=2000&amp;month1=6&amp;day1=1&amp;year2=2000&amp;month2=8&amp;day2=3&amp;category=a&amp;id=20000628a04&amp;keyword1=&amp;keyword2=</a><br />\n<br />\n誤診男童重金屬中毒　醫生兩項專業失德罪成(楊樂賢)<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/2668/%E8%AA%A4%E8%A8%BA%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E9%87%8D%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%85%A9%E9%A0%85%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%B1%E5%BE%B7%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F2668%2F%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%25A0%2585%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=7cd99cdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/2668/%E8%AA%A4%E8%A8%BA%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E9%87%8D%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%85%A9%E9%A0%85%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%B1%E5%BE%B7%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90</a><br />\n<br />\n誤切病人門靜脈及膽管   醫生金振明被停牌1年<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20110622/50022596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20110622%2F50022596&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=0449262a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20110622%2F50022596&h=af83d10c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20110622/50022596</a><br />\n<br />\n西醫林連美失德罪成<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170408/00176_044.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170408%2F00176_044.html&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=51abeefe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170408/00176_044.html</a><br />\n<br />\n四女西醫宣傳拉客疑失德 陳斐嘉<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20090409/00176_051.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20090409%2F00176_051.html&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=42dcc664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20090409/00176_051.html</a><br />\n<br />\n被裁失德 梁英傑除牌緩刑<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160813/00176_050.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160813%2F00176_050.html&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=a641e824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160813/00176_050.html</a><br />\n<br />\n雙氧水靜脈注射　延誤送院病人不治 西醫梁錫超專業失德停牌18月<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20040226/3880155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20040226%2F3880155&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=96bde05c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20040226%2F3880155&h=d81572ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20040226/3880155</a><br />\n<br />\n病人治汗臭燒燶腋下　西醫失德除牌1月緩6月 (陳東飛)<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170502/bkn-20170502125851467-0502_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170502%2Fbkn-20170502125851467-0502_00822_001.html&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=36353739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170502/bkn-20170502125851467-0502_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n七旬婦接受上門診症後亡裁死因不明　死因裁判官：涉案醫生非誠實可靠證人 (司徒敬豪)<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190718/s00001/1563429459029/%E4%B8%83%E6%97%AC%E5%A9%A6%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%87%E5%BE%8C%E4%BA%A1%E8%A3%81%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E-%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98-%E6%B6%89%E6%A1%88%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%9D%9E%E8%AA%A0%E5%AF%A6%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.